name: UIPrintError.Code
desc: Constants that specify the print error code.

items.name: case noContent
items.desc: UIKit hasn’t assigned a print formatter, page renderer, or printing item to print.

items.name: case unknownImageFormat
items.desc: An image is in a format that UIKit doesn’t recognize for printing.

items.name: case jobFailed
items.desc: An internal error occurred with the print job.
